&gt; &gt; QueueAssignmentPolicy.modules but currently modules are built into the
&gt; &gt; heritrix jar -- whereas heritrix.properties is not -- so adding new
&gt; &gt; policies would be a bit of a pain (You&#39;d add the new policy then have
&gt; &gt; to remake the jar).
